<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Sunhare Digital Marketing</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome for icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #F9FAFC;
            color: #333333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #1A73E8;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        header nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        header nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .hero {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #1A73E8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .services {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin: 50px 0;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .service-card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        .service-card h3 {
            color: #1A73E8;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .service-card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .service-card a {
            color: #FF5722;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .service-card i {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #1A73E8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #1A73E8;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        footer .social-icons a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        footer .social-icons a:hover {
            color: #FF5722;
        }
        footer .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        footer .contact-info button {
            background-color: #FF5722;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        footer .contact-info button:hover {
            background-color: #E64A19;
        }
        .contact-info a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>Sunhare Digital Marketing</h1>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Welcome to Sunhare Digital Marketing</h1>
            <p>Your trusted partner for SEO, Social Media, Email Marketing, and more. Let us help you grow your online presence.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="services">
            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                <h3>Advanced SEO</h3>
                <p>Boost your search engine rankings with targeted SEO strategies.</p>
                <a href="/services#advanced-seo">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
                <h3>Social Media Management</h3>
                <p>Strengthen your brand’s presence on popular social platforms.</p>
                <a href="/services#social-media-management">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                <h3>Email Marketing</h3>
                <p>Engage your audience with personalized email campaigns that convert.</p>
                <a href="/services#email-marketing">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-ad"></i>
                <h3>PPC Advertising</h3>
                <p>Maximize your ROI with expertly managed pay-per-click ad campaigns.</p>
                <a href="/services#ppc-advertising">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i>
                <h3>Website Development</h3>
                <p>Design and develop responsive, user-friendly websites to enhance your online presence.</p>
                <a href="/services#website-development">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-pencil-alt"></i>
                <h3>Content Marketing</h3>
                <p>Create high-quality content that drives traffic and converts visitors into customers.</p>
                <a href="/services#content-marketing">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                <h3>Conversion Rate Optimization</h3>
                <p>Optimize your website to convert visitors into leads and sales.</p>
                <a href="/services#conversion-rate-optimization">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                <h3>Reputation Management</h3>
                <p>Protect and manage your brand’s online reputation with proactive strategies.</p>
                <a href="/services#reputation-management">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-video"></i>
                <h3>Video Marketing</h3>
                <p>Engage your audience with compelling video content that promotes your brand.</p>
                <a href="/services#video-marketing">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-paint-brush"></i>
                <h3>Graphic Design</h3>
                <p>Create eye-catching designs for your brand's marketing materials and digital platforms.</p>
                <a href="/services#graphic-design">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Sunhare Digital Marketing Agency. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        
        <div class="social-icons">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.twitter.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>Connect with us for more details.</p>
            <button>Contact Us</button>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>